prometheus helm repo on github
- "https://prometheus-community.github.io/helm-charts/

The following components in the helm chart were disabled as they were not needed for the AMP.
- alertmanager
- prometheus-kube-state-metrics
- prometheus-prometheus-node-exporter

Per AWS instructions, only prometheus server is needed
- prometheus-server


FOR REMOTE WRITE TO AMP, ADDED THE FOLLOWING UNDER SERVER:
server:
  ## Prometheus server container name
  name: server
  remoteWrite:
    - url: https://aps-workspaces.${AWS_REGION}.amazonaws.com/workspaces/${WORKSPACE_ID}/api/v1/remote_write 
      sigv4:
        region: ${AWS_REGION}
      queue_config:
        max_samples_per_send: 1000
        max_shards: 200 
        capacity: 2500

NEED TO ADD THIS UNDER SERVICE ACCOUNT. THIS IS THE ROLE USED:
serviceAccounts:
  server:
    create: true
    name: "prometheus-service-account"
    annotations: 
      eks.amazonaws.com/role-arn: ${IAM_PROXY_PROMETHEUS_ROLE_ARN}


FOR WINDOWS TOLERATION THIS WAS ADDED:
  tolerations:
    - key: node.kubernetes.io/os
      operator: Equal
      value: windows
      effect: NoSchedule